Welcome to Aerospace Fasteners Incorporated

Aerospace Fasteners Inc. is a leading distributor of aircraft fastening hardware for commercial and military aerospace applications. We offer a wide variety of high-quality aircraft hardware and parts, that feature everything from bolts to rivets to every small piece in-between. We are also happy to offer specialty services including vendor managed inventory, product kitting, consignment services, and more.

As trusted aerospace hardware distributors in Palestine, TX, we are AS9100/ISO 9001:2015 certified and compliant with all International Traffic in Arms Regulation (ITAR) regulations. We are proud to have been serving the aerospace industry since 1979. Companies such as Boeing and Raytheon trust us because, like them, we understand that even the smallest components are critical. If you are looking for trusted aircraft hardware suppliers, look to our company to provide superior products that are designed and stocked by reputable manufacturers. Contact us today at (903) 723-0693 to learn more about our products and services.
